Name: Konrad the Rocket
About the game: Our GLORIOUS NATION needs you! You will test the secret weapon that will guarantee our SUPERIORITY ! The Project Rocket! The tests aren't easy and we don't expect your survival, but that's how HEROES are born! Play as Konrad, a humble worker that is being forced to test a secret weapon. Features: Project Rocket: It is actually a jetpack 75 levels Original soundtrack Inspired by George Orwell's 1984 20 achievements Made by one person
